<div class="white-spacer"></div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Meet our team</h1>
      <div class="flourish">
        <%= image_tag "rsz_nb_butterfly-01.png", alt: "alttext", class: "avatar-tiny", id: "img-hr" %>
      </div>
      <div class="white-spacer"></div>
        <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="false">
          <div class="carousel-inner" style="margin:0px auto">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <%= image_tag "ange.png", alt: "Angelique Bradford", class: "avatar-bordered-employee" %>
              <div>
                <h2>Angelique Bradford</h2>
                <h3>Founder & Commercial Director</h3>
                <div class="white-spacer"></div>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                    Find out more
                  </a>
                <div class="white-spacer"></div>
                <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                  <p>
                    Angelique has over 20 years’ experience at helping build businesses from within. She excels at finding outstanding talent, matching skills and personality to roles, and making sure that individuals are truly following the career path right for them. Previous positions within both sales and marketing bring a wide commercial breadth, ensuring that she can help New Beginnings’ clients both develop and maintain their broader business vision.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Her passion is for people and she loves it “when a plan comes together” for both client and candidate. Outside of work, her life revolves around her son, horse, dogs, a cat and the team think she might be a chicken whisperer! Her husband has long realised he is at the bottom of the pecking order…
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <%= image_tag "lydia.png", alt: "Lydia Stimpson", class: "avatar-bordered-employee" %>
              <h2>Lydia Stimpson</h2>
              <h3>Marketing Extraordinaire</h3>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                  Find out more
                </a>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                <p>
                  A social butterfly, Lydia loves the diversity of working with people from all over the world, both colleagues and guests who have enhanced her perspective on life. As a child, her formative years were spent in Ireland, from where she gained her love of music, festivals, fun and travel. She has a passion for the creative arts and brings to New Beginnings her innovative approach. She supports the marketing and design aspects of the brand.

                </p>
                <p>
                  Not only a whizz with all things SEO, Lydia also helps support our clients to achieve the transformation they seek both in their business and their careers. Lest we forget, her other passion is her dog who takes up the rest of her time!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <%= image_tag "marni.png", alt: "Marni Scott", class: "avatar-bordered-employee" %>
              <h2>Marni Scott</h2>
              <h3>The Organiser</h3>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                  Find out more
                </a>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                <p>
                 Marni is the Executive Assistant to Rose De Winter. She performs various office management duties and recruits new talent for New Beginnings. Prior to joining the company, Marni recently graduated from Bournemouth University after studying Communication and Media.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <%= image_tag "olic.png", alt: "Oli Cassell", class: "avatar-bordered-employee" %>
              <h2>Oli Cassell</h2>
              <h3>Design Wizard</h3>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                  Find out more
                </a>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                <p>
                  Oli is New Beginnings' head of design, ensuring consistency across the board with NBC’s identity. Oli is currently based in Manchester and has over 5 years experience working both in-house for global brands and with highly regarded agencies in Manchester, Mallorca and Glasgow.
                </p>

              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <%= image_tag "olim.png", alt: "Oli Marriott", class: "avatar-bordered-employee" %>
              <h2>Oli Marriott</h2>
              <h3>Web Developer</h3>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseExample" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                  Find out more
                </a>
              <div class="white-spacer"></div>
              <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
                <p>
                  Oli is New Beginnings' web developer, based in Amsterdam. Oli has a background in product but has recently converted to programming and helping Ange with her technology phobia.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      <div class="white-spacer"></div>


    </div>
  </div>

